        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "step-9-next-steps",
      "title": "Next Steps",
      "description": "You've seen the layout. Read the project readme for usage and the contributor guide for build commands and conventions. Try the quick-start flow — register a repository, then start the daemon — against any public repo. Finally, explore the examples directory for containerized deployments, including the Cloudflare sandbox SDK integration.",
